"FIRE!" - In what has been a fun little project recently, I managed to start a fire with sticks! #bowdrill ü§ì It seems to be one of those things in which the first time is a huge hurdle to get over. After that, it is all just refining technique. Also thank you to mentors @thecabinlife and Zach (pics 4 & 5). Zero chance of doing it without your guidance. 
.
Also note: no cabins or houses were burned down in the creation of these fires. Fire alarms may have been set off however... ü§£
